QuestData.Title: Bow to the Highlord
QuestData.Description: I am unworthy to even carry a message directed at you, sir. Please forgive me for this indulgence. Overlord Mor'ghor has requested your presence in his chambers at once!
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak to Overlord Mor'ghor at Dragonmaw Base Camp in Shadowmoon Valley.
QuestData.RewardText: You are the first highlord of the Dragonmaw, $N. The master himself has chosen to come here to promote you.
